org.swerverobotics.library.interfaces

Class IBNO055IMU.Parameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • IBNO055IMU.Parameters
  • Enclosing interface:
    IBNO055IMU

    public static class IBNO055IMU.Parameters
extends java.lang.Object
    Instances of Parameters contain data indicating how a BNO055 absolute orientation sensor is to be initialized.
    See Also:
    IBNO055IMU.initialize(Parameters)
